Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:18.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的愿望  摇曳的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:29.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让飞雪滑过脸颊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:36.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}挥之不去的后悔  紧系过去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:39.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北风的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一触即散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:50.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夹杂着寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:58.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越过了眼中的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:06.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在想给你的旋律  遥指着初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:14.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼凑出的未来  手指间露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:22.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要实现在此看见的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:28.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}约定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:47.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君は今も覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:51.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夜の丘に集まっては
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:56.80,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}幼い夢を話し合ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:01.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}季節巡ってもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:12.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}私たちは「運命」なんてものを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:18.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}振り返ることなど知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星に願いを込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:33.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}想いを解き放つとき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:38.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ah　いつか夢見たあの日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:44.03,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}帰れる気がするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いにしえの扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:53.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}開けることができたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:58.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ah　私たちは手を繋げる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:03.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}そう信じていたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:08.64,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だから私ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}皆の願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:18.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}託した光はそして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:31.74,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}空の一面に今散らばった
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:47.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你如今是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:51.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夜晚集合在小山上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:56.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}倾述着儿时的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:01.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}四季再次周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:12.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我们对自己的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:18.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}从不曾后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只知道要一直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向星星许下愿望后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:33.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}等到思念解放之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:38.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}仿佛又能再次回到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:44.03,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如梦似幻的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}永恒不变的那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:53.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}终能渐渐打开之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:58.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相信我们必将会是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:03.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}手牵着手一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:08.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以我才会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}收集起大家的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:18.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}并将它们化为星光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:31.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}泼洒在这片天空中
