Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:43.48,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(45,270)}「流星雨之夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由我来做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔我也做一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没焦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也在成长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫诺艾尔来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  托爸爸的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来的时候  一定让她尝尝爸爸的拿手菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可能会晚点回来  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得保持联络通畅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌云先生  乌云先生  快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于今晚的流星雨  今年可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也发生过这样的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比那个时候更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道柚季也在强忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚来天文台集合  大家一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  凑太  之后要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合在天文台…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乃乃香所相信所决定的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯生姜汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要实现诺艾尔的欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  今天晚上大家在天文台集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天文台看流星雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我静静呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再跟我扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(298,252)\1c202020\bord0\fs10\frz-30}朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是朋友  你明白一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你明白一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季这个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢自己的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太也很珍重自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春这个女生  看见别人受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像自己受伤一样难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比任何人都更怕寂寞  有点固执
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却相信只要自己忍耐下去  大家就都能幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我们帮汐音拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是大家都能开心欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔跟我说  这个愿望太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个愿望里面  也包含着汐音的欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟诺艾尔说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  我想大家会集合在天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨  好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家什么时候会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  不要擅自闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是住在同一个房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在分房了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  分房是在我受伤的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再跟凑太说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季真的可以接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是明摆着的吗  不跟哥哥说话也没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中的要难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是诺艾尔她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗  呼唤飞碟那天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早上为了一点小事  我们吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  我们根本没吵过架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道该怎样和好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  向飞碟许愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和她们永远好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  和你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在湖边的那一天  我们看见的飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想  是不是诺艾尔实现了我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我的愿望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跟哥哥  跟大家吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也希望能够很快和好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  这次该轮到我们去实现诺艾尔的愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在呼唤飞碟的时候许下了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们永远都能是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能明白大家的心情  能在大家身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许也是托了诺艾尔的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定会在天文台等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会再也见不到了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此  为什么还能露出这样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不悲伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也见不到乃乃香和大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当大家高兴的时候  心里就会暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当大家悲伤的时候  又觉得阵阵刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当大家欢笑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔就会想  是不是实现大家的愿望了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和最喜欢的大家一起欢笑着离别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞碟  飞碟  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我能一直喜欢乃乃香和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经实现了我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能拒绝你的请求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)\an8\fs20\1c141139\3cAAAAAA}（禁止入内）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们也刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拆穿会死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}算了算了  茶都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}乃乃香  诺艾尔  快来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}你发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}太好了  大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}怎么了  又说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我想给大家介绍个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}初次见面  我叫户川汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}那种天气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}在等流星雨的时候来照张相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}大家都来照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}相机借我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我会全部都拍下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我们也去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}不要抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}必须要好好地…照不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经是朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔给我的最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很珍视
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  泡温泉真愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又大又暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会大家再一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能对乃乃香重展笑颜  也是多亏了诺艾尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔一直在守护着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生康复了  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了凑太的帮助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你帮助了诺艾尔  怪兽先生才能康复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢凑太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柚季和凑太让我注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望的真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽做些赶走飞碟之类…过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对不会忘记诺艾尔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔也不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香给了我很多很多美好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…必须要欢笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定  一定要欢笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的话  你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  汐音  柚季  凑太  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是  流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来看流星雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明非常高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该非常高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在欢笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔对大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经有心理准备了吧
